Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明天亮了卻還是很困
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明天亮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的天亮了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許天還沒亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛確實是天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:05.65,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,590)\fad(500,500)}初雪火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯你走路好快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為好冷所以想早點到學校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是特別的冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒命饒命饒命！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  這裡是搞笑劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曬到日光可以精神變好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶的影子部分不太暖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陽的地方就是舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太舒服了都變得慵懶不想動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「土豆」這個詞真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「土豆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「土豆」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是「土豆」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  用煮爛的土豆啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要去掉皮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給穿得單薄的小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔過去的話你會生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該會吧…畢竟很燙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想扔扔看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔給你包含有「悄悄給你了」「請你吃」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那反正要給的話就好好拿個好吃的給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  某種意義上燙呼呼的很好吃啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭討厭  不要來這種反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴走族取名叫「土豆」怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛呀  日本第一可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的很厲害哦  全關東第一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為這暖和天氣的原因吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  櫟井同學怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小相  她沒事的  完全沒問題喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體有沒哪裡出了問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土…豆…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂相川  剛才的笑聲是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是櫟井她們？那聲音有夠大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  好像是因為「土豆」的梗而笑趴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三個傢伙果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷冷冷冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開暖氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫…暖氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你朋友嗎？  這麼得瑟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖爐它…是個好傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為太費電了  所以也算是個敗家的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期幾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？為什麼突然冒出個「原來如此」來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼…星期四是不是有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是「土豆」的感覺  熱氣騰騰的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是土豆也有週六的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真的啊」是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今日主題  星期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六  Saturday是從農業之神——薩杜恩一詞而來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:22.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,630)}Saruen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說嘛  所以土豆是星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是土豆真的很熱氣騰騰的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才就一直在說的「mokumoku」是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「mokumoku」形容熱氣騰騰狀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那第2第4就是星期四啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那星期四是什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四  Thursday來自北歐神話裡的雷神托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家用遊戲機發售日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多週刊漫畫的發行日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好日子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:11.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}具注曆是平安時代流行於奈良的一種曆書，起源於我國。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在具注曆中似乎把星期天寫成「密」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「ミール」在古粟特語中是星期天的意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是把「ミール」轉寫成的漢字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點邪惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  下一個密要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  下一個密現在有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密做點什麼吧密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  密啊密的吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用蔡勒公式的話  就可以從日期直接計算出星期幾來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那1999年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  用蔡勒式計算就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那2020年的1月1日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也用蔡勒公式計算就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天作為休息日  而且人們以星期為標準而生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在明治時代引入西曆後出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那個呢  美容院什麼的要怎樣才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠猜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像是星期二所以休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說以前的人有星期幾的概念嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的人都是家裡蹲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子同學  拜託你做總結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把邊框的裝飾留著可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那總結就是
